The company is having it's annual employee ping pong (table tennis) tournament. We need an application that will collect employee names, email addresses and shirt sizes.
We wan't the application to automatically assign players to a team at the moment the user signs up.
We would also like to have a page where users can go to see the team rosters.

Since this app will be hosted on our company intranet portal (and our portal team will be handling the integration portion of this app), there will be no need to develop a custom authentication system.
We would like the app to be responsive. Mobile designs have been supplied if time allows, but for now, simply having a fluid desktop design is the minimum requirement
